videos.headline: Mayfield picked off on Oklahoma's first drive
videos.description: Cowboys CB A.J. Green jumps the rout and intercepts Baker Mayfield's pass.

videos.headline: Mayfield throws 49-yard TD to Flowers
videos.description: Baker Mayfield finds Dimitri Flowers for a 49-yard Oklahoma touchdown.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Johnson makes 60-yard grab
videos.description: Mason Rudolph throws a 60-yard strike to Tyron Johnson for a first down at the Sooners' 15-yard line.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State WR outjumps defender for TD catch
videos.description: Mason Rudolph throws the ball up to where only Marcell Ateman can catch it for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Mayfield delivers a 55-yard pass to Andrews
videos.description: Baker Mayfield finds an open Mark Andrews for a 55-yard catch to Oklahoma State's 20-yard line.

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Badet sneaks into the corner of the end zone
videos.description: Jeff Badet turns on the jets for a 5-yard touchdown to put the Sooners back on top of the Cowboys.

videos.headline: Oklahoma uses trick play for 16-yard gain
videos.description: Off the double reverse, Baker Mayfield finds Trey Sermon for 16 yards.

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Brown shows patience in 36-yard catch and run
videos.description: Baker Mayfield throws a short pass to Marquise Brown, who runs between blockers for a 36-yard catch and run.

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Mayfield uses stiff arm to get into end zone
videos.description: Baker Mayfield gets the edge and stiff-arms his way into the end zone for a 7-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State gets to red zone with 52-yard pass
videos.description: Mason Rudolph hooks up with James Washington for 52 yards to put the Cowboys in the red zone.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Hill runs up the gut for TD
videos.description: Justice Hill finds a hole up the middle for a 6-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Mayfield finds Brown for third TD pass of half
videos.description: Baker Mayfield finds a streaking Marquise Brown, who takes it 84 yards to the house.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Lacy makes 32-yard grab
videos.description: Mason Rudolph throws to Chris Lacy down the sideline for a 32-yard catch.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Rudolph throws second TD pass
videos.description: Mason Rudolph connects with Marcell Ateman, who creates separation for a 2-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Anderson breaks tackle for TD
videos.description: Rodney Anderson takes a hit in the backfield, but manages to stay on his feet for a 14-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Rudolph adds to trio of TD passes
videos.description: Mason Rudolph throws a beautiful ball to James Washington for a 35-yard touchdown pass.

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Mayfield hooks up with Jones for 30-yard gain
videos.description: Baker Mayfield finds Mykel Jones over the middle for a 30-yard catch to to put Oklahoma in Cowboys' territory.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Hill rushes for second TD of half
videos.description: Justice Hill rushes to the outside for 30 yards for a touchdown to tie the score at 38-38 right before halftime.

videos.headline: 76 points scored in wild first half of Bedlam
videos.description: Oklahoma State scores late in the second quarter to tie Oklahoma at 38 in a half full of big offensive plays.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (76 points scored in wild first half of Bedlam) 2017/11/04 SOTFULL ESHEET

videos.headline: Oklahoma forces Rudolph fumble
videos.description: Kenneth Mann knocks the ball loose from Mason Rudolph and Oklahoma's Ogbonnia Okoronkwo recovers the ball at the Cowboys' 10-yard line.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Hill trucks defender for big gain
videos.description: Justice Hill barrels through an Oklahoma defender for a 34-yard run.

videos.headline: Oklahoma forces second Rudolph turnover
videos.description: Will Johnson picks off Mason Rudolph for the Sooners' second forced turnover of the quarter.

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Andrews makes 36-yard catch
videos.description: Baker Mayfield completes a 36-yard pass to Mark Andrews to put the Sooners in Oklahoma State territory.

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Mayfield throws fourth TD
videos.description: Baker Mayfield finds an open Rodney Anderson down the sideline for a 43-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Johnson beats defender for TD
videos.description: Mason Rudolph hooks up with Tyron Johnson for a 33-yard touchdown catch.

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Mayfield's 5th TD pass goes for 77 yards
videos.description: Baker Mayfield throws a 77-yard strike to Marquise Brown in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Ateman displays beautiful footwork to complete catch
videos.description: Marcell Ateman just gets his foot down in bounds for an 18-yard catch after the Cowboys elect to go for it on fourth down.

videos.headline: Rudolph's fifth TD sets Bedlam combined record
videos.description: Mason Rudolph completes an 18-yard touchdown pass to Tyron Johnson to close the gap to 55-52, setting the most points in the history in the rivalry.

videos.headline: Oklahoma 's INT gets called back for targeting
videos.description: Tre Brown intercepts Mason Rudolph's pass, but it gets called back after a targeting call against Will Johnson. After review, Johnson was ejected for targeting.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State turns it over on downs late in 4th quarter
videos.description: Mason Rudolph over throws Tyron Johnson on 4th and 8 with a minute to go to give the ball back to Oklahoma.

videos.headline: Oklahoma pads lead with late 53-yard score
videos.description: Trey Sermon dodges defenders for a 53-yard touchdown to give Oklahoma a 62-52 lead late in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Oklahoma prevails in high-scoring showdown
videos.description: In a wild edition of Bedlam that saw 114 points, Baker Mayfield put up 598 yards and five touchdowns in the Sooners' thrilling win over the Cowboys.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Oklahoma prevails in high-scoring showdown) 2017/11/4 ESHEET SOTFULL
